w perfectly over dresses – ideal for a wedding. Equally, its length invites you to add a belt and cinch it in at the waist for pairing with wide-leg trousers. A really smart buy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"tweed-jacket-with-frayed-ends\"\u003eTweed jacket with frayed ends\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"d2d7c054-6430-40de-9f0d-7345ebc22b56\" data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.ImageBlockElement\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"img-9\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/d6f25839edd793ccae7d1593903cac14b955e66d/0_0_1500_2098/master/1500.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 660px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/d6f25839edd793ccae7d1593903cac14b955e66d/0_0_1500_2098/master/1500.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/d6f25839edd793ccae7d1593903cac14b955e66d/0_0_1500_2098/master/1500.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/d6f25839edd793ccae7d1593903cac14b955e66d/0_0_1500_2098/master/1500.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/d6f25839edd793ccae7d1593903cac14b955e66d/0_0_1500_2098/master/1500.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 320px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/d6f25839edd793ccae7d1593903cac14b955e66d/0_